text: D3D may refer to: * DIII-D (tokamak) (pronounced 'D3D'), a tokamak located at San Diego, California * Direct3D, Microsoft's graphics rendering scheme * Dolby 3D * Duke Nukem 3D or Duke3d, a first person shooter video game from 1996 * China Railways HXD3D, a type of electric locomotive in China
title: D3D
